{"tid":805364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 應該要守望相助啦","createTime":"2018-09-03T17:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T10:51:53.000Z","uid":143960,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b70a2db701f95fb73328316cd1aa76a81ea6d055","tid":805364,"uid":143960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T17:21:10.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚跑跑下步見到有警犬喺度抄牌，我心諗你益班仆街警犬，不如我做下好心行過去八達通泊車咪錶幫佢哋續費。啊屌你老味，行到去拍第一個嘅時候個警犬即刻啤住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我咪串下佢，我問佢：「阿Sir，乜我依家有犯法咩？你做咩審犯咁望住我，係咪我阻住咗你交數搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。<br />\n   最後條警犬死死地氣過嚟問我攞身分證，算，我一個人俾你抄身分證有乜所謂，睇你個柒頭抽唔到人車牌，唔知點解突然間好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n   個PC仔抄完我身分證最後死死地氣走，我就知道又贏一仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係果句啦香港人互相幫下手唔會死嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e649fa17cb9aa2cac77f85aa706e93b7eaaad50a","tid":805364,"uid":143960,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"呼籲大家見到都要幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f4c0b3539c4446545364a55b0d5d95768b02ee","tid":805364,"uid":8028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da0f6294774e3d7aec5dfdec998dd9c716a66a8","tid":805364,"uid":143960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16f4c0b3539c4446545364a55b0d5d95768b02ee","tid":805364,"uid":8028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T18:03:06.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\